title: Jeb Bush’s Poll Numbers Continue To Plummet
text: Jeb Bush has had anything but a successful campaign so far. While the former governor of Florida remains the favorite among establishment Republicans, GOP voters are not interested. In August, the son and brother of former presidents was polling at around 13 percent. Now, he’s at around 6 percent. That’s a pretty impressive decline and...
